HEADWORD: Second-class
<hw>Sec"ond-class`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of the rank or
degree below the best or highest; inferior; second-rate; <as>as, a
<ex>second-class</ex> house; a <ex>second-class</ex> passage; a
<ex>second-class</ex> citizen</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

